## 🏗️ Architecture

```plaintext
[ PDF/Image Input ]
        ↓
[ Image Classification ]
        ↓
[ Document Understanding ]
        ↓
[ OCR + ChatGPT NLP ]
        ↓
[ Structured JSON ]
        ↓
[ UiPath Dispatcher – Queues ]
        ↓
[ UiPath Performer – Data Validation & Entry ]
        ↓
[ MySQL / Power BI / Final Output ]



